descriptionHtml:
Following a recent rockfall in Riverwood, an ancient tomb has been exposed and on further investigation it appears to be an ancient Tomb of a Dragon Priest, containing a maze.  Many brave adventures have entered this tomb searching for Dragon Treasure, but only one poor soul has emerged, stricken by nightmares of strange goings on, of monsters within the giant, dark, overgrown maze.  

If you dare accept the challenge, enter here with your best lanterns, sword and most vital of all, a fearless pure heart as you could come out owning the best of what is within ..... if you come out alive that is ....

Update werewolves have taken over the maze

Tome is over the river from Riverwood
author: Me
